A worker puts chrysanthemum flowers into containers for baking at an agriculture ecological garden in Wuzhong Village of Qiaoxi District, Xingtai, north China's Hebei Province, Nov. 17, 2019. The development of chrysanthemum planting industry in Qiaoxi District of Xingtai has acted as a way to boost locals' income. (Xinhua/Zhu Xudong)   

